    <item>
      <title>印度维斯塔拉航空公司因减薪而取消更多航班 飞行员愤怒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/vistara-cancels-flights-as-airline-struggles-with-crew-shortage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位知情人士透露，塔塔集团和新加坡航空共同拥有的印度维斯塔拉航空公司在飞行员因计划减薪而集体请病假后，取消了数十个航班。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/vistara-cancels-flights-as-airline-struggles-with-crew-shortage</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 05:56:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
